{"tid":476727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[創新] Uber隱瞞半億用戶資料被盜","createTime":"2017-11-22T09:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T07:16:32.000Z","uid":17103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9a6c267306e7d919f0f197cc115804b3a1fc86","tid":476727,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"Uber隱瞞半億用戶資料被盜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/sites/sbs.com.au.yourlanguage/files/styles/full_mobile/public/protect_yourself_from_online_scams_-_getty_images_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fyourlanguage%2Fsites%2Fsbs.com.au.yourlanguage%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Ffull_mobile%2Fpublic%2Fprotect_yourself_from_online_scams_-_getty_images_3.jpg&h=79b70b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n共享型汽車接載服務 Uber 承認，該公司的伺服器在較早前被黑客入侵，超過半億用戶資料亦被盜取。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國彭博新聞報導，黑客在去年十月透過入侵 Uber 的伺服器，成功取得 5,700 萬 Uber 客戶及司機的個人資料，包括其姓名、電郵地址及電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n但報道指，公司未有即時向用戶及當局通報事件，<span style=\"color: red;\">反而向黑客繳交 13.2 萬澳元款項，以求黑客刪除相關資訊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUber將引入無人駕駛汽車<br />\n<br />\n共享型汽車接載服務 Uber 表示，即將購入一批富豪汽車，希望引入無人駕駛汽車投入業務。<br />\n<br />\nUber 公司的管理層承認，當時的做法未如理想。<br />\n<br />\n該公司的行政總裁 Dara Khosrowshahi 向彭博新聞表示，有關事故絕對不應發生，今後將會改變公司應對相關事件的策略。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">據報，黑客入侵的手法並不複雜：黑客使用編碼網頁 Github 攻破兩名 Uber 技術人員的帳戶，並找到一些載有客戶資料的伺服器及登入伺服器的資料。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑客取得 Uber 用戶資料後，向公司進行勒贖。<br />\n<br />\n這次並非 Uber 公司首次被揭發未有匯報資料外洩；該公司去年由於資料外洩，被紐約律政部長處罰 26,000 澳元。"},{"pid":"eb0764026f0ff6796bb9ec93131255f27c609234","tid":476727,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c818395daee9661f308b5931eccd6926880a0b8a","tid":476727,"uid":38550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"乜將server login 放上Github 咁高技術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed9ae7049efca6ba7facf8b43ceff63f6d89f24","tid":476727,"uid":30347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"原來Uber open source㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c9a9e7c04deea87eef116f206c3c3e8469f814","tid":476727,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"又有一堆IT狗失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cd1f16fd43e8403cf76f3c945f3e106a6c72cc","tid":476727,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來Uber open source㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實 Uber 前已經有 Source Code 放上網比的士佬同客用 .. 可以任意 download .. <br />\n<br />\nUber 可以彈出係靠 CEO 籌旗有金主先打通全世界"},{"pid":"588e4a7b13fa50e5425c32cdfdf36d6eb4b3e5c5","tid":476727,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來Uber open source㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實 Uber 前已經有 Source Code 放上網比的士佬同客用 .. 可以任意 download .. <br />\n<br />\nUber 可以彈出係靠 CEO 籌旗有金主先打通全世界</blockquote><br />\n佢寫私人GitHub<br />\n應該係工程師自己上傳做嘢<br />\n就好似當Google drive咁"},{"pid":"699be7f2723521e115286c4748add0a80bd3c0d2","tid":476727,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blo